---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/PageLayout.astro"

const LAST_UPDATED = "July 22, 2026"
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Effectful Technologies Inc. handles your data on the Effect website"
>
  <section class="relative pt-16 pb-12 md:pt-24 md:pb-16">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-295 px-4">
      <p class="mb-3 font-mono text-sm font-medium tracking-wide text-zinc-400 uppercase">
        // Legal
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tighter text-white md:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-sm text-zinc-400">
        Last updated: {LAST_UPDATED}
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-24 md:pb-32">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-295 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-12">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
            This website is operated by Effectful Technologies Inc. (&ldquo;Effectful,&rdquo;
            &ldquo;we,&rdquo; or &ldquo;us&rdquo;). We keep data collection to a minimum. We do not
            use advertising trackers, cross-site profiling, or analytics cookies.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-tighter text-white">1. Analytics</h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            We use PostHog in cookieless mode to understand how this website is used.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            PostHog may collect usage information such as page views, clicks, browser and device
            information, and referring pages. We use this information to understand general website
            usage and improve the site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-tighter text-white">
            2. Information you give us
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            If you email us or submit one of our forms, we receive the information you provide,
            typically your name, email address, and message.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            We use this information to respond to your request and retain it only for as long as
            reasonably necessary.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            Some forms are hosted using Google Forms. When you submit a form, Google may process
            information under its own privacy policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-tighter text-white">
            3. Cookies and local storage
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            We do not use analytics or advertising cookies.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            The site may store limited functional preferences in your browser&rsquo;s local storage,
            such as your theme choice.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-tighter text-white">4. Hosting</h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            This website is hosted using third-party infrastructure, including Vercel. Our hosting
            providers may process technical information such as IP addresses, request details, and
            browser or device information to deliver, operate, and secure the website.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            Their respective privacy policies apply to this processing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-tighter text-white">5. Third-party services</h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            Some pages link to or embed content from third-party services, such as YouTube, Discord,
            GitHub, our events calendar, and our merchandise store.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            When you interact with those services, their own privacy policies apply.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-tighter text-white">6. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            Questions about this policy or your data? Contact us at{" "}
            <a
              href="mailto:contact@effectful.co"
              class="text-white underline decoration-zinc-600 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-white hover:decoration-zinc-400"
            >
              contact@effectful.co
            </a>
            .
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-tighter text-white">
            7. Changes to this policy
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
            If we change how this website handles data, we will update this page and the date at the
            top.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
